{
  "texts": [
    "Comparison to base judges and fine-tuning them: Our results on absolute rating prediction tasks are reported in Table 1.",
    "We start with Summarize from Feedback dataset and Prometheus base judge.",
    "The MSE of the LS judge (2.626) is less than a half of that of the base judge (6.346), and the lowest of all methods.",
    "This is expected because we optimize the MSE (Section 4.1).",
    "The LS judge has also the lowest MAE."
  ]
}